<inglise>(1) Sections 531-565 of the ESSR Civil Code (ENSV Teataja (2) 1964, 25, 115; 1968, 46, 341; 1969, 30, 295; 1970, 37, 332; 1973, 9, 68; 1973, 44, 389; 1973, 53, 465; 1974, 28, 247; 1977, 6, 72; 37, 424; 1980, 31, 490; 1985, 27, 451; 1986, 19, 251; 1988, 6, 68; 1988, 25, 295 and 296; 1989, 17, 203; Eesti Vabariigi Teataja (3) 1990, 20, 300; RT 1990, 12, 128; 1992, 33, 418; 49, 615; RT I 1993, 72/73, 1021; 1994, 25, 406; 53, 889; 63, 1065) are repealed. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Notariaadiseaduse (RT I 1993, 45, 640; 1994, 5, 49; 93, 1571; 1995, 61, 1028; 1996, 23, 456) &sect; 59 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Section 59 of the Notaries Act (RT I 1993, 45, 640; 1994, 5, 49; 93, 1571; 1995, 61, 1028; 1996, 23, 456) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 59. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 59. </inglise>
<eesti>P&auml;rimisasjade lahendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Settlement of succession matters </inglise>
<eesti>Notarid lahendavad p&auml;rimisasju p&auml;rimisseaduses s&auml;testatud juhtudel ja t&auml;htajal.". </eesti>
<inglise>Notaries shall settle succession matters in the cases and during the term provided for in the Law of Succession Act.". </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Riigil&otilde;ivuseaduses (RT 1990, 11, 118; RT I 1995, 36, 465; 57, 981; 58, 1005; 61, 1028; 87, 1540; 1996, 3, 56) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The State Fees Act (RT 1990, 11, 118; RT I 1995, 36, 465; 57, 981; 58, 1005; 61, 1028; 87, 1540; 1996, 3, 56) is amended as follows: 1) Subsection (12) is added to &sect; 4 of the Act worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) seaduse &sect; 4 t&auml;iendatakse l&otilde;ikega 12 j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>"(12) Upon receipt of information from the succession register, courts and notaries are exempt from payment of state fees." ; </inglise>
<eesti>"(12) P&auml;rimisregistrist teabe saamisel on riigil&otilde;ivu maksmisest vabastatud kohtud ja notarid." ; </eesti>
<inglise>2) Subclause 54) is added to clause 8) of Appendix 1 of the Act, worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>2) seaduse lisa 1 punkti 8 t&auml;iendatakse alapunktiga 54 j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>"54) For issuance of information concerning one person from the succession register, 50 kroons." (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>
